      <h1 class='title'>Shropshire Central Services (Staffing)</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 c105WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_105ws' title='Col. 105WS &mdash; HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 c105WS' name='column_105ws' href='#column_105ws' rel='bookmark'>105WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-05235'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_528'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-paul-marsden' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_528' title='Link to this speech by Mr Paul Marsden' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-paul-marsden" title="Mr Paul Marsden">Mr. Paul Marsden</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-05235">To ask the Secretary of State for Health how many staff worked in Central Services for Shropshire County Council in each year since 1997. [132292]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-05236'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_529'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-nick-raynsford' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_529' title='Link to this speech by Mr Nick Raynsford' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-nick-raynsford" title="Mr Nick Raynsford">Mr. Raynsford</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-05236">I have been asked to reply.</p><p id="S6CV0412P0-05237">The number of staff working in Central Services for Shropshire County Council in each year since 1997 is tabled:
          <table>
          <tr>
          <td><span class="italic">Year</span></td>
          <td><span class="italic">Central Service</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>1997</td>
          <td><sup>1</sup>&#x2014;</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>1998</td>
          <td><sup>1</sup>&#x2014;</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>1999</td>
          <td>412</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>2000</td>
          <td>414</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>2001</td>
          <td>418</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>2002</td>
          <td>403</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>2003</td>
          <td>415</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td><sup>1</sup> Comparable figures for 1997/98 are not readily available. Significant changes arose at that time because of Local Government re-organisation, when some 35 percentage of the Council's staffing transferred to Telford & Wrekin Council.</td>
          </tr></table>
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
